{"tid":2191703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新巴車長向阻路警響咹，反遭警屈「快速駕駛危及路旁警」被捕","createTime":"2020-09-06T15:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T16:47:37.000Z","uid":201027,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29d9fb9d87f5becb2994700e9f4883a08b48f5d3","tid":2191703,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:09:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">呢班黑警大撚晒</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200906/BUCSNGQFKRATDAPCJDUXS2TU2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200906%2FBUCSNGQFKRATDAPCJDUXS2TU2E%2F&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4gogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=38148952\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200906%2FBUCSNGQFKRATDAPCJDUXS2TU2E%2F&h=2b608c5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200906/BUCSNGQFKRATDAPCJDUXS2TU2E/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有網民號召今午於九龍油尖旺一帶遊行，防暴警在多區重兵戒備。下午4時許，油麻地彌敦道一架新巴970路線巴士遭截查，防暴警更上車檢查乘客身分證和車長位置。戴了「豬嘴」的車長被帶到一旁，約一小時後被押上警車。有傳媒報道，車長疑不滿去路被阻，向警方響咹，故警員截停該架巴士截查。警方至晚上8時許在Facebook專頁發帖，稱該名車長「快速行駛」，「危及」在路旁執勤的警務人員安全，故以「危險駕駛罪」拘捕他。<br />\n<br />\n不過警方當時的Facebook直播，卻與其聲明有些出入。片段中，一名警員指控該名司機「挑釁」警方、駕駛期間「無故」響咹，「影響」警方工作，亦會「挑起」在場人士情緒。另有警員向司機表示，其駕駛行為及態度危及「道路使用者」，屬危險駕駛。警員之後將該名司機帶上警車。「巴士台」Facebook引述消息，指一眾新巴車長因不滿警方濫捕，即日起發動按章工作抗議，歡迎同業加入。<br />\n<br />\n事發約下午4時40分，油麻地彌敦道近眾坊街有至少40名市民被警截查至少1小時，被截查人士其後被全數帶上警方兩架旅遊巴，其間一名被截查的女子不適由白車送院。防暴警截查時，一架970路線新巴途經上址，停泊在對開的彌敦道中線。防暴警其後登上巴士，檢查乘客身份證和司機位置。城巴至下午4時45分安排另一架970接走該批乘客；該名戴了「豬嘴」的970新巴車長則被警員帶到一旁調查。<br />\n<br />\n車長被查逾句鐘後，被多名交通警押上涉事巴士，之後再被押上警車。有傳媒報道，疑車長向警方響咹，故警車截停該架巴士截查。<br />\n<br />\n警方至晚上在facebook專頁發帖稱，涉事新巴沿彌敦道駛至近文明里時，快速行駛，一度非常貼近站在路旁正在執勤的警務人員，危及人員安全，並指由於該名巴士司機駕駛態度十分危險，警員遂截停該名司機。西九龍總區交通部其後到場調查，以危險駕駛罪拘捕車長。警方正翻查相關行車記錄片段及附近閉路電視片段，案件現交由西九龍總區交通部負責調查。<br />\n<br />\n翻查現場直播片段，該名被截查女子被抬上緊擔架床前，涉事970仍未出現。之後女子被送上白車時，現場曾聽到有響咹聲音，970已停在中線。在970未駛到該位置前，已有多名防暴警員在慢線戒備。"},{"pid":"18ad8430200d1f27553882086220deb5c1ee7d0a","tid":2191703,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:13:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">呢班黑警大撚晒</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f481f025bebe77948476103ca6723fc549223b62","tid":2191703,"uid":154738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"會唔會罷工"},{"pid":"6fe468a955feaa6d297e60135ceaa3e825dd96fa","tid":2191703,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f481f025bebe77948476103ca6723fc549223b62","tid":2191703,"uid":154738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"會唔會罷工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"希望新巴車長會帶頭罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db42958f25915d1cd5a2bdbca258ea6a8052df23","tid":2191703,"uid":19640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f010df62c0ea4520168fbfcc0c41a70d8da422","tid":2191703,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db42958f25915d1cd5a2bdbca258ea6a8052df23","tid":2191703,"uid":19640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063b687291d5a695852a89aa7861a5b8f1c852e9","tid":2191703,"uid":274149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:57:27.000Z","msg":"支持，其他行業是否要加入？"},{"pid":"dabf311bb0dc8b02aa4168939de238f64a087c7a","tid":2191703,"uid":19640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3faa12bdee67cfd457a851b59e6194a7d363098","tid":2191703,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"063b687291d5a695852a89aa7861a5b8f1c852e9","tid":2191703,"uid":274149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:57:27.000Z","msg":"支持，其他行業是否要加入？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"短時間好難令最鍾意返工嘅香港人罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}